    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/d4c9a50e0fbd083e808cce23ed71b7cb.poster.avif?t=1770741040\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/d4c9a50e0fbd083e808cce23ed71b7cb.webm?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/d4c9a50e0fbd083e808cce23ed71b7cb.mp4?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>学习足以改变世界的咒语，让它们脑洞大开的效果为你所用</u></strong></h2>踏上满是奇思妙想的解谜之旅，探秘各式神奇咒语，每种咒语都有专属的特殊能力，足以改变你周围的世界。<br><br>随游戏进程不断深入，掌握更多规则，探寻各式深奥又奇妙的用法，让每一条咒语为你所用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/2633dd04e39261b721ab2738b09c997e.poster.avif?t=1770741040\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/2633dd04e39261b721ab2738b09c997e.webm?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/2633dd04e39261b721ab2738b09c997e.mp4?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>帮助名为LOK的生物开疆拓土</u></strong></h2>遁入神奇的魔法LOK宇宙，这个迷人的世界由引人瞩目的手绘美术风格和颇具禅意的原声曲目交织而成，做好准备，在这里流连忘返吧。<br><br>机制易上手，玩法脑洞大，《LOK Digital》诚邀各位玩家每天都回来看看，这里还有程序生成的各式谜题，能将游戏机制的广度和深度体现得淋漓尽致。<br><br>每当你拼出魔法咒语，名为LOK的生物就会诞生。它们只能生活在涂黑的方格里，由此一来，每解决一道谜题，你都是在帮助它们开疆拓土、散播文明。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/736cc6b39a0731edfe5d1f736e32b4e6.poster.avif?t=1770741040\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/736cc6b39a0731edfe5d1f736e32b4e6.webm?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207440/extras/736cc6b39a0731edfe5d1f736e32b4e6.mp4?t=1770741040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>游戏特色：</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>符合直觉的游戏机制，还有多种特殊咒语等你发现、学习 <br></li><li>优美的手绘美术风格与颇具禅意、令人陶醉的原声曲目<br></li><li>在100+个谜题关卡中学习LOK语言的各种细微差异<br></li><li>在精心打造的日常谜题模式中展现你对游戏机制的深刻理解 <br></li><li>基于备受好评的解谜图书《LOK》改编而成<br></li><li>由发行过《怪兽远征》、《Cosmic Express》、《Bonfire Peaks》等作品，屡获殊荣的解谜游戏专业团队Draknek &amp; Friends发行</li></ul>",
